snippet.title: Daemonologie Launch Date Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3048140/Daemonologie/

This trailer is to announce the actual release date and update with some of the art changes since the last one.

Daemonologie is a short folk horror story about the Scottish witch trials. You play the role of a witch finder. Speak to the locals and sort their truths from their lies. On the last morning a witch must hang, best you know who by then.
